ut space                                                                                FAT image full                                                  Remove host-only training files or grow the disk image when FAT image assembly runs out of space.                                                                                               qemu logs capture compile run copied evidence files before trusting emulator result                                                                             QEMU logs                                                       Capture compile logs, run logs, and copied evidence files before trusting an emulator result.                                                                                                   hardware validation run same batch path real dos copy return.txt back compare checksums logs                                                                    Hardware validation                                             Run the same batch path on real DOS, copy RETURN.TXT back, and compare checksums and logs.                                                                                                      memory error dos free conventional unloading tsrs loading drivers high using smaller profile                                                                    DOS memory error                                                Free conventional memory by unloading TSRs, loading drivers high, or using a smaller profile.                                                                                                   batch menu offer numbered choices validate input keep branch short reversible                                                                                   Batch menu                                                      Offer numbered choices, validate the input, and keep each branch short and reversible.                                                                                                  